import fs from"fs-promise";import Promise from"bluebird";import path from"path";import{getEnv}from"./manager";import startShell from"./startShell";export default function use(t){return getEnv(t).then(([t,e])=>startShell(e,t))}export function vars(t){return getEnv(t).then(([t,e])=>{let r=`\n# Biome config\nexport BIOME_SHELL=true\nexport BIOME_PROJECT="${e}"\nexport BIOME_NVARS="${Object.keys(t).length}"\n\n# Project variables\n`.trim()+"\n";for(let e in t)r+=`export ${e}="${t[e]}"\n`;if(Object.keys(t).length>0){r+="function envoff {\n";for(let e in t)r+=`  unset ${e}\n`;r+="}"}return r})}